** TB1(10A)
0 CANCEL
1 CHANGE
2 ADD
3 INQUIRY                                          JW7
** ER (60) ........2.........3.........4.........6
E-01 ENTER 0, 1, 2 OR 3 FOR UPDATE#
E-02 ENTER DELIVERY CODE !
E-03 DELIVERY CODE NOT FOUND !
E-04 DELIVERY CODE WAS CANCELLED !
E-05 DELIVERY CODE EXISTS !
